Localization.Name: Greycat Industrial
Localization.Description: A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.

Localization.Name: Tru Barrier Hazard Suit Cinnabar
Localization.Description:
Carrying Capacity: 1K µSCU
Temp. Rating: -5 / 32 °C

Guard yourself from toxic environmental hazards with the TruBarrier Hazard Suit, constructed from industrial-grade fabric and coated with a multi-layered, laminated polymer that offers a broad range of chemical protection without sacrificing mobility. The encapsulated design provides full-body protection from direct contact with dangerous materials when worn with its accompanying mask.
